  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Safety and Preliminary Efficacy of IDCT, a Treatment for Symptomatic Lumbar Intervertebral Disc Degeneration</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Double‑Blinded, Vehicle‑ and Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Safety and Preliminary Efficacy of IDCT in Subjects With Single‑Level, Symptomatic Lumbar Intervertebral Disc Degeneration</official_title>
